\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1.3}{\ignorespaces \textit {Left:} Side view of the Milky Way, depicting its components and satellite galaxies, notably the Large and Small Magellanic Clouds (LMC and SMC). \textit {Right:} Spatial distribution of galaxies within the Local Group, dominated by the Milky Way and Andromeda galaxies. Source: Wikipedia - Pablo Carlos Budassi (left) and Andrew Z. Colvin (right)\relax }}{4}{figure.caption.7}%
